    <item>
      <title>伊隆·马斯克计划在宾夕法尼亚战场为特朗普竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/elon-musk-to-campaign-for-donald-trump-in-pennsylvania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，埃隆·马斯克计划本月在宾夕法尼亚州为唐纳德·特朗普竞选，该州可能决定总统大选的最终胜出者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/elon-musk-to-campaign-for-donald-trump-in-pennsylvania</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 20:16:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和哈里斯利用播客争取选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/trump-harris-embrace-podcasts-in-2024-election-for-tuned-out-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普和卡玛拉·哈里斯全力投入播客，提供约会建议、个人理财技巧和深入流行文化的节目正在吸引对这两位总统候选人的采访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/trump-harris-embrace-podcasts-in-2024-election-for-tuned-out-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 20:02:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默向政治低头，任命摩根·麦克斯威尼为其首席助手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/who-is-morgan-mcsweeney-and-why-did-uk-s-starmer-back-him-over-sue-gray</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯尔·斯塔默执政的前三个月过得并不顺利，他的政府饱受捐款争议、内讧和英国公共财政日益低迷的困扰。周日，他终于向工党压倒性胜利的缔造者求助，试图纠正局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/who-is-morgan-mcsweeney-and-why-did-uk-s-starmer-back-him-over-sue-gray</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:54:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lululemon 创始人价值 6000 万美元的房子因选举标志被毁坏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/lululemon-founder-s-60-million-house-defaced-in-british-columbia-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁 Lululemon Athletica Inc. 创始人奇普·威尔逊 (Chip Wilson) 价值 6000 万美元的豪宅已成为涂满涂鸦的导火索，象征着加拿大省级选举的两极分化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/lululemon-founder-s-60-million-house-defaced-in-british-columbia-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:47:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚副总统反对弹劾，不会辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/kenya-s-deputy-president-to-fight-impeachment-in-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚副总统里加蒂·加查瓜表示，他将于周二出席国民议会，就其违反宪法的指控进行辩护，并拒绝辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/kenya-s-deputy-president-to-fight-impeachment-in-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 16:46:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
