    <item>
      <title>以色列与哈马斯开战一周年，多条战线同时作战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-says-it-intercepted-hamas-rockets-as-war-marks-one-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防军称，他们拦截了哈马斯和其他伊朗支持的组织向特拉维夫发射的大部分火箭弹。经过一年的战争，双方周一在多个战线上的战斗进一步升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-says-it-intercepted-hamas-rockets-as-war-marks-one-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 15:56:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯导弹击中第二艘粮食船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ukraine-says-russia-missile-hit-ship-loaded-with-corn-for-export</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据基辅基础设施部称，俄罗斯周一向一艘满载乌克兰谷物的船只发射了一枚弹道导弹，这是两天内第二起此类事件，造成一人死亡，五人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ukraine-says-russia-missile-hit-ship-loaded-with-corn-for-export</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 13:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯和特朗普纪念哈马斯袭击以色列一周年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/harris-trump-mark-oct-7-milestone-with-mideast-still-aflame</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一年前的 10 月 7 日，哈马斯武装分子攻入以色列南部，此后，其引发的动乱和不确定性继续影响着整个中东地区 — — 以及白宫的激烈角逐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/harris-trump-mark-oct-7-milestone-with-mideast-still-aflame</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
